                                                * PC Alchemy
                                                * PDB (without header).

@ENDNODE

@NODE Save "Save"

You can save a file under the @{"format" LINK Format} PetitChimiste.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Synthese "Synthese"

This part allows you to obtain a 3D synthesis view of the molecule
Its very interresting, because with a wireframe view, you can't
distinguish wich atome is in front or in back.
At present time, 256 colors are used.
Remember that the memory allocated for rendering is function of the
screen size. For example: 640*512*8 => 3.72 MO

@ENDNODE

@NODE Quit "Quit"

Terminates the application.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Format "MOLEC3D file format"

@{b}Exemple:@{ub} A cube

@{b}LABEL@{ub}    @{b}X@{ub}       @{b}Y@{ub}       @{b}Z@{ub}

C1      0.0     0.0     0.0
C2      0.0     0.0     0.5
C3      0.0     0.5     0.0
C4      0.5     0.0     0.0
C5      0.0     0.5     0.5
C6      0.5     0.5     0.0
C7      0.5     0.0     0.5
C8      0.5     0.5     0.5

C1-C2           @{b}C1 connected with C2@{ub}
C1-C4
C1-C3
C6-C3
C7-C8
C2-C5-C3        @{b}C2 connected with C5 and C5 connected with C3@{ub}
C2-C7-C4
C4-C6-C8-C5

@ENDNODE

@NODE Calc "Calculs"

The @{b}TextField@{ub} allows you to have some calculations.

 @{b}Example:@{ub}

     C1-C2      Gives the @{b}length@{ub} between the twice carbon atomes
                C1 and C2.
                Lengths are gived in @{b}picometre@{ub} (1pm = 1E-12m).


     C1-C2-C3   Gives the angle @{b}angle@{ub} between thethree carbon atomes
                C1,C2 and C3.
                Les angles sont donnés en @{b}degrés@{ub} and @{b}minutes@{ub}.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Keys "Keys"

@{b}Rotations:@{ub}

    @{b}Axe X:@{ub}             7   angle -= step (fast - slow)
                       8   angle  = 0
                       9   angle += pas de calcul

    @{b}Axe Y:@{ub}             4   angle -= step
                       5   angle  = 0
                       6   angle += pas de calcul

    @{b}Axe Z:@{ub}             1   angle -= step
                       2   angle  = 0
                       3   angle += step


@{b}Déplacements:@{ub} Arrows

The molecule is moved in the arrow direction.

@{b}Zoom:@{ub} +/-

@ENDNODE

@NODE Control "Control Window"

 @{b} Reset @{ub}          Replace les réglages par défaut

 @{b} With names @{ub}     Visualisation with or without names.
 @{b} Without names @{ub}
 @{b} Compact model @{ub}   @{"Choice of the representation" link Synthese}.
 @{b} Exploded model @{ub}

 @{b} Fast @{ub}           The step for the Visualisation.
 @{b} Slow @{ub}

 @{b} Manual @{ub}         (V.A.O.N.C)
 @{b} Automatic @{ub}      Visualisation Assisted Or No by Computer

 @{" Calculations " LINK Calc}  The TextField where you can do calculations

 @{" Keys " LINK Keys}  To shift the molecule

@ENDNODE

@NODE Visual "Visualisation Window"
    Do not select !
    The @{"Control window" LINK Control} have to stay selected.
@ENDNODE

