@NODE WhatsNew "What is new ?"

v2.1
- Chunky pixels on GFX cards or Akiko.
- A real memory management improvement.
- An acceleration.

v2.01
- Memory management improvement: redering 10% faster.
- A localised installation script.

v2.00
- Real time movies.
- Some bugs fixed.
- A way to version 2.01.

v1.45
- Some bugs fixed in memory management.

v1.43
- A new mode for the rendering called 'Compact'.
- Dynamic allocation of memory.
- Faster loading.
- 'ESCAPE' to stop the rendering.
- Some bugs killed.

v1.40
- A new fast synthesis fonction using much RAM.
- Some changes appeared in menus.
- The PDB format (without header) is now supported .

v1.31
- Some bugs corrected in the localisation.
  Complete traduction in spanish. Thank you Dámaso D. Estévez :-)

v1.3
- 1.29 -> 1.3, because lot of things have been made since v1.24
  Morover, the two compiled programs have been optimised.

v1.29
- Big optimisation of the rendering.
  A bug fixed in the choice of colors.

v1.28
- Support of screen promotion.
- Tooltypes

v1.27
- graphic fonctions rewritten
- matrix fonction rewritten.

v1.26
- A module of 3D synthesis.
- The mathematic library is now IEEE (a bug fixed)

v1.25
- Lot of small bugs fixed.
- direction of deplacement changed.

v1.24
- PC Alchemy Transparent loading.
- Localised.
- Compiled in english.

See @{"History" LINK History}.

@ENDNODE
